      • attachStatesAndLabels

        private void attachStatesAndLabels(Model model,
                                   ModelExplicit modelNew,
                                   java.util.List<java.lang.String> propNames,
                                   java.util.List<java.util.BitSet> propBSs)
        Attach a list of states to the minimised model by adding a representative state from the original model. Also attach information about the propositions (used for bisimulation minimisation) to the minimised model, in the form of labels (stored as BitSets).

        modelNew - The minimised model
        propNames - The names of the propositions
        propBSs - Satisfying states (of the minimised model) for the propositions
